Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.26,0:00:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.86,0:00:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.49,0:00:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.15,0:00:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個充滿神秘的黑衣組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.08,0:00:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是旅行劇團的正式表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件和劇本一同解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.78,0:00:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.68,0:00:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個去參觀轉學到小蘭班上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.88,0:01:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊東玉之助率領的旅行劇團排練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.29,0:01:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現他們這幾個人暗地裡各懷鬼胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.72,0:01:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.39,0:01:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.40,0:02:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件發生時全體演員正在舞臺上面排練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.99,0:02:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矇騙了在觀眾席上的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與劇團演員的眼睛犯下這起案子的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.14,0:02:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在這些人當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.73,0:02:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行劇團殺人事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.88,0:02:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上遇害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.59,0:02:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近石鐵夫先生所屬的這個旅行戲團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就寄宿在記者身後的這間旅館裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.98,0:02:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前該團的少年團長正在警局裡面接受相關的詢問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 妳哥哥回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.52,0:02:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天晚上開始你就沒有睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之今天晚上可以好好的睡一覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.39,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把這當成自己家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.33,0:03:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我們跟你父親是老朋友嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 這個時間怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間怎麼會到劇場來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.15,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.90,0:03:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定很擔心妳哥哥對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.89,0:04:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 柯南你在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也擔心你哥哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 這件事情你就交給我好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是回旅館比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你想趕我回去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.24,0:04:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這個時間小孩子出來不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.00,0:04:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南和我不是一樣大嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥會在哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.20,0:04:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是舞臺那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.16,0:04:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.74,0:04:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 兇手應該沒有跑遠才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 快叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.76,0:04:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.77,0:04:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系江小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊東玉之助 因為頭部遭到重擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.31,0:05:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意識昏迷的情況之下被緊急地送到醫院急救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於死在奈落裡面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}奈落:舞臺的地下室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.19,0:05:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個劇團擔任演員兼經理的 荻原系江小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是掉落到奈落裡摔死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.03,0:05:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ITOE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真面目被揭穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌晨零點我在舞臺等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.38,0:05:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 死者手裡好像握著什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子 她是為這個來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.56,0:05:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也有一張跟那一樣的紙條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這個地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南他可是第一個發現者哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.05,0:06:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.60,0:06:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體周圍怎麼有這麼多的垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼快回去睡覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為現在幾點鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.26,0:06:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.64,0:06:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉之助現在都受傷了 你還把他當成犯人看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.68,0:06:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.41,0:06:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為兇器上有他的指紋嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有其他人的指紋嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.90,0:06:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還有其他幾個團員的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.80,0:06:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻沒有死去的系江小姐的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是系江小姐對玉之助進行攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.72,0:06:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果一不小心就掉到奈落裡面摔死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是玉之助他絕對不是那種會殺人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.15,0:06:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 我們到醫院去看看他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.46,0:06:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 那柯南他們就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉之助現在拒絕所有人拜訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是重要嫌犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想小惠應該在旁邊照顧他才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只想把花送過去而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.72,0:07:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子現在還昏迷不醒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.71,0:07:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是心意的問題 不用你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.05,0:07:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你剛才說玉之助是重要嫌犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.29,0:07:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他有可能自己把自己打到意識昏迷嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個問題嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.59,0:07:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據醫生表示他的外傷倒不怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.79,0:07:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能是因為精神上的影響 所以現在還沒有恢復意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 如果是精神上的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.74,0:07:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能是他在行兇之後逃避現實的一種表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才認定他就是第一重要嫌犯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人去作案現場的字條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據筆跡鑑定結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.42,0:07:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是玉之助所寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 他還向劇團裡的每個成員都發了一張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼要找系江小姐過去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過據說她正在極力地存錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.68,0:08:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且聽說她還私吞了劇團不少錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是根本無法溝通的劇本作家近石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是破壞劇團財務的經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團長自然想對付他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一般來說 會因為這種原因去殺人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我拿罐啤酒過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不到時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.99,0:08:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼執著嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對解決案子會有幫助的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 還有一包零食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.22,0:08:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 近石先生的磁片找到了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.77,0:08:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說警方在玉之助的房裡找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.60,0:08:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面資料全被消掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.11,0:08:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被丟在房裡面的垃圾桶裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.79,0:08:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料被消掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.77,0:09:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想裡面大概有什麼對他不利的資料吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是丟在那裡不是一下子就被發現了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 你到外面去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心情一不好就會趕我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是成事不足的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.72,0:09:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 再拿一罐過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡根本就找不到你說的那種碎屑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 有木頭的地方可能會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 死者是在別的地方遇害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後被丟到奈落去的 這也有可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.82,0:09:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個顏色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那是三夾板的碎屑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.18,0:09:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.38,0:09:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.94,0:09:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面沾了血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大小跟奈落差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.95,0:09:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連顏色也跟舞臺木板很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這是陷阱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個厚度0.3公分的三夾板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中間還被切了幾刀好讓它更容易折斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到死者摔死了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒就立刻把木板藏到那裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼玉之助接著就打他自己嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.52,0:10:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其實那天我跟小惠從旅館一直跟在他的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他應該沒有時間設下這個陷阱才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.15,0:10:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉之助有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為兇手另有其人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻進行安排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.23,0:10:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.99,0:10:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經成功的潛入旅館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇團的成員全部都在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最接近樓梯的這個房間的田島先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊看電視一邊在休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.74,0:11:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井小姐這邊正在保養她的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.41,0:11:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在死去的近石先生房間的村木先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.06,0:11:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在整理房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣了 請回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 你們接下來就可以回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.90,0:11:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.64,0:11:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又來這套了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.08,0:11:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杯戶市立醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.51,0:11:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.07,0:11:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.17,0:11:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.07,0:12:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.57,0:12:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙的身手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是江戶小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來江戶小子就躲在劇團裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉之助在發現這一點之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想利用表演把他給逼出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.97,0:12:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 近石先生早在他之前就注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕近石先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就以這個藉口勒索江戶小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才會殺害近石先生把他的磁片內容消掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉之助在確認了江戶小子就躲在劇團裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這宗殺人案件發生之後就感到後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才會發出那樣的紙條來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉這麼晚打擾你 田島先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你今天晚上有沒有出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.79,0:13:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有劇團裡的人今天晚上都沒有出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.02,0:13:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個 這麼說柯南也在這了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.11,0:13:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛才到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.78,0:13:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這三個小鬼果然還在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還做了不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是江戶小子 一定就是他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還沒有證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺 實在太興奮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有柯南一個人可以留下 我實在不能接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.56,0:13:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.32,0:13:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為柯南有監護人陪著嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.43,0:13:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 而且這次可以坐警車不就足夠了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天辛苦你了 毛利先生 喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 我現在正在工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.22,0:13:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只喝一杯會有什麼影響呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.69,0:14:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有心情喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間都已經不夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.88,0:14:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近石先生被殺的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時間犯案的只有兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.39,0:14:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.38,0:14:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說體格足以攻擊玉之助的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.72,0:14:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在座的各位 請你們集中到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.59,0:14:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道兇手是什麼人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.02,0:14:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害了近石先生和荻原系江小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.74,0:14:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還兩度襲擊玉之助的這個兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就在我們之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.01,0:14:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.09,0:14:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直一派胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.29,0:14:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別激動 先聽聽看他怎麼說也無妨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上多虧了毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.46,0:15:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能夠保住玉之助的一條命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.09,0:15:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據今天晚上到醫院襲擊玉之助的兇手的身手來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.25,0:15:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該就是江戶小子本人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.03,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這一切案件的起點也就在於江戶小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.63,0:15:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起江戶小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家應該都知道他擁有時代劇演員靈活的身手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.22,0:15:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個在日本國內到處犯案的竊盜犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這半年來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.11,0:15:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們身邊應該多多少少有東西遺失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這點 我跟百合都已經被警方調查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕對是清白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都有完美的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠進行特技表演的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.38,0:15:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們劇團裡面只有兩個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個都是由田島先生教出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.19,0:15:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是田島先生的腰會痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.22,0:15:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有三年沒有表演過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.46,0:15:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次 你們團長玉之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.57,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主張將江戶小子的故事搬上舞臺表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.31,0:15:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 近石先生所寫出來的劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.77,0:16:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻不是玉之助原先計劃所要表現的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.74,0:16:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近石先生他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.01,0:16:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會中途把故事內容改寫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.50,0:16:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近石先生在調查有關江戶小子案件的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.85,0:16:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到他的真面目是誰的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我猜測 近石先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以改寫劇本為條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對江戶小子進行金錢勒索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江戶小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田島健三先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說田島先生是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…他說他的腰會痛這全是騙人的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.13,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想三年前他的腰會痛應該是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.77,0:16:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從半年前開始我想他的腰傷應該已經完全好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.83,0:16:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言 我實在是聽不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.17,0:16:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能不能麻煩你繼續在這坐幾分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田島先生 你就是兇手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.75,0:16:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.48,0:16:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前一切狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.39,0:17:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都明顯顯示出你就是真正的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.97,0:17:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說那天唯一有機會殺害近石先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為劇團裡面演員不夠的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.43,0:17:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們三個都分別一人分飾二角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.01,0:17:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟百合小姐是在後臺更換衣服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村木先生因為必須快速的登場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在跑向奈落的途中換衣服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.86,0:17:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為米花劇場的奈落特別深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在規定時間之內站上道具台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.46,0:17:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞臺旁邊換上原有衣服的村木先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.96,0:17:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時根本就沒有任何時間可以犯案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 近石先生的房間就在後臺的旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.57,0:17:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了換衣服經過的田島先生和百合小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有足夠的時間殺害近石先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.82,0:17:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是系江小姐的死是個意外啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找她出去的那張紙條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的"ITOE"說明了一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.36,0:17:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我們都收到了一張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.09,0:18:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼會這麼認為呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個名字的寫法是團長的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.40,0:18:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是說伊太郎寫給江戶小子的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.85,0:18:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那個"ITOE"並不是羅馬字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是 "I to E"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.52,0:18:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是伊太郎致信給江戶小子的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.85,0:18:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你們團長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.05,0:18:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是為了什麼給每個團員都發了一張呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我哪會知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.78,0:18:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到團長對我有恨我就一肚子氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就去喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說那張紙條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.50,0:18:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給真正的江戶小子的話又怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想玉之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.39,0:18:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經很確定殺死近石先生的就是江戶小子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.91,0:18:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是誰才是江戶小子他還不能確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才會把紙條發給所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.45,0:18:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 系江小姐誤以為那張紙條是要給她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到了劇場裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.12,0:18:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻掉進了兇手設好的陷阱裡 就這樣摔死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.17,0:19:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉之助在進入劇場之後馬上也受了傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 玉之助那天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有時間擺設那張三夾板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有時間將它藏起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場裡面當時除了他們兩個其實另外還有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.71,0:19:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是奈落裡面還找到另外一張紙條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就認定是我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.03,0:19:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我真的有時間殺害近石先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能因此證明我就一定殺了他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.04,0:19:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合也有時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田島先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為出現在醫院裡的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體格身影都和你非常的相像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體格相像就能說我是兇手了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太好笑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 那麼目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.02,0:19:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你再將近石先生電腦上面的指紋檢查一遍好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們在事件發生之後就檢查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼結果都沒有發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還查什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.41,0:19:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為兇手在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.27,0:20:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該又有使用過那台電腦才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.23,0:20:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的是要把他從近石先生房裡找到的磁片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再確認一次的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.61,0:20:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是想警方根本不可能再檢查一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就空手操作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木老弟 找鑑識課來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.16,0:20:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.84,0:20:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近石和系江都是我殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.68,0:20:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我就是江戶小子的近石先生死了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.17,0:20:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來很放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是團長又發了那張紙條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.16,0:20:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.16,0:20:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只覺得腦子裡面一股氣往上衝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.02,0:20:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有仔細思考過就到舞臺設了陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.00,0:20:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 系江死了之後我就以為沒有事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匆忙把三夾板藏起來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.03,0:20:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻發現團長站在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.24,0:20:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有想到我會對團長下手 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田島先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是我錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我沒有演那齣戲就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.75,0:21:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.56,0:21:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我並沒有要用那出戲來趕走你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望你能夠早點彌補罪過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向警方自首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.21,0:21:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.37,0:21:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請你原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.74,0:21:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時真的急昏了頭 才會對你出手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.86,0:21:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很抱歉 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.23,0:23:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.27,0:23:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場裡面也做了修整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.28,0:23:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出的劇目內容也大幅度地做過了修改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.71,0:23:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉之助還是帶著傷登臺演出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.61,0:23:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我們這些外行人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.46,0:23:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也特別地登臺演出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.12,0:24:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.49,0:24:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7.6毫米的子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.24,0:24:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全金屬外殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.02,0:24:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.54,0:24:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,競技場無差別恐嚇事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.28,0:24:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.12,0:24:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著藍色帽子的小男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.60,0:24:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.78,0:24:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭祝新年快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.47,0:24:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年不管是電視、電影或是少年Sunday 請多多指教哦
